item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】ALAC - Sol Maria - Eladio Carrion
item.description:
Another one
Puerto Rican trap sensation Eladio Carrión showcases a new level of depth and range on his latest release, Sol María. This heartfelt tribute to his mother adds a personal touch to his ever-evolving style, highlighting his strong family values and his determination to make his parents proud. Despite this introspective turn, Carrión maintains his signature boldness and charisma, delivering his unmistakable flow with unwavering confidence.
